<!-- Header Partial -->
<%- include('../partials/header') %>

    <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-100 to-blue-300 py-16 mt-20">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
            <!-- Page Title and Introduction -->
            <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 mb-6">Discipline</h1>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 mb-12 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
                We believe that discipline is a key element to fostering a positive
                and productive learning environment. Our discipline policy encourages respect, responsibility, and
                integrity among students.
            </p>

            <!-- Discipline Guidelines Section -->
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-12">

                <div
                    class="p-8 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500 ease-in-out hover:transform hover:scale-105">
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Respect for Others</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
                        Students are expected to treat their peers, teachers, and staff with respect. This includes
                        listening to others, using polite language, and refraining from any form of bullying or
                        disrespectful behavior.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div
                    class="p-8 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500 ease-in-out hover:transform hover:scale-105">
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Punctuality</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
                        Students should arrive on time for classes, meetings, and events. Punctuality is an important
                        part of maintaining an organized and efficient learning environment.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div
                    class="p-8 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500 ease-in-out hover:transform hover:scale-105">
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Integrity</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
                        Honesty is paramount in our school. Students are expected to adhere to the principles of
                        integrity, avoiding cheating, plagiarism, or any form of dishonesty.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div
                    class="p-8 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500 ease-in-out hover:transform hover:scale-105">
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Collaboration</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
                        Working together is an essential skill. Students are expected to collaborate effectively with
                        peers, respect diverse opinions, and contribute positively to group work.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div
                    class="p-8 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500 ease-in-out hover:transform hover:scale-105">
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Respect for School Property</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
                        Students should respect school property and take care of their surroundings. This includes
                        maintaining classrooms, equipment, and common areas, as well as reporting any damages.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <!-- New Dress Code Discipline -->
                <div
                    class="p-8 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500 ease-in-out hover:transform hover:scale-105">
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Dress Code</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
                        Students are expected to follow the school's dress code, which promotes a neat, respectful, and
                        professional appearance. Clothing should be modest, appropriate for school activities, and not
                        disruptive to the learning environment.
                    </p>
                </div>

            </div>

            <!-- Discipline Consequences Section -->
            <div class="mt-16">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 mb-6">Consequences for Misconduct</h2>
                <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                    We have a clear and fair system for handling misconduct. Students who violate the school rules may
                    face consequences such as warnings, detention, or suspension depending on the severity of the
                    offense.
                </p>

                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-10">
                    <div
                        class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-500 ease-in-out">
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Minor Violations</h3>
                        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600">
                            <li>Late arrival</li>
                            <li>Disruptive behavior</li>
                            <li>Not following dress code</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <div
                        class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-500 ease-in-out">
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Major Violations</h3>
                        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600">
                            <li>Fighting</li>
                            <li>Cheating or plagiarism</li>
                            <li>Substance abuse</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Call to Action Section -->
            <div class="mt-12">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 mb-6">Our Commitment to Respectful Behavior</h2>
                <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                    We are committed to providing a safe and respectful learning environment for every student. We ask
                    our community to follow these guidelines to maintain a positive atmosphere for all.
                </p>
                <a href="/contact"
                    class="inline-block bg-blue-800 text-white py-3 px-6 rounded-lg shadow-md hover:bg-blue-900 transition duration-300 ease-in-out transform hover:scale-105">
                    Get in Touch
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Footer Partial -->
    <%- include('../partials/footer') %>